    p.mb-8.text-lg.text-white.md_max-w-sm.lg_max-w-md Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Atque reprehenderit dolores modi totam iure sed magnam ab animi ducimus autem? Eos totam consequuntur quibusdam deserunt dignissimos ipsa sint unde nobis.
    button.px-6.py-4.bg-blue-600.text-white.hover_ring Get Started Now
  //- From Principal Section
  //- Programs Section
  section.p-4.sm_px-10.py-8.flex.flex-col.items-center
